                                    </div><div id="wb_element_instance10_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="wb_element_instance11_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="wb_element_instance12_1" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><img alt="" src="gallery/Picture1-ts1613891972.png"></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance13_1" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal"><span style="color:rgba(3,2,3,1);"><strong>You remember the excitement of attending live events -  concerts, clubs and at your favorite entertainment venues, don't you?</strong>  </span></p>
                                                    </div></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance14_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="wb_element_instance15_1" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><img alt="" src="gallery/Picture2-ts1613891976.png"></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance16_1" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal"><strong><span style="color:rgba(5,5,5,1);">We're bringing some of that excitement and entertainment back to you virtually, through your favorite streaming platform.</span></strong></p>
                                                    </div></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance17_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="wb_element_instance18_1" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><img alt="" src="gallery/Picture3-ts1613891980.png"></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance19_1" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal"><strong><span style="color:rgba(5,5,5,1);">It actually will be better because our audiences and fans are going to be able to interact with the artists, and so much more!</span></strong></p>
                                                    </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="wb_element_instance20_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="wb_element_instance21_1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="wb_element_instance22_1" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h5 class="wb-stl-subtitle" style="text-align: center;">Want To Get Involved?</h5>

                                        <p class="wb-stl-normal"> </p>

                                        <p class="wb-stl-normal"><strong>Interested in advertising on The GIG or auditioning? We're looking for sponsors, brand promotions and talent to audition to be a part of our program, Just click the link below and a pre-addressed email will open for you to request more infomation. Please specify what your interest might be so that we can forward your information to the proper individual, who will get back to you in a timely manner.</strong></p>
